Package: auto-ssh-tunnels
Version: @VERSION@
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: autossh, openssh-client, netcat-openbsd, python3, python3-yaml, systemd
Maintainer: nedlosster <nedlo@yandex.ru>
Description: SSH tunnel manager with YAML config
 Manages multiple persistent SSH tunnels via a single YAML configuration.
 Generates systemd services, health-check watchdog, and logrotate configs.
